




title, situation, task, action, result, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (1, 3, 'Time Management', 'Tell me a time you worked under pressure?', 'Throughout the duration of the coding bootcamp, I worked as a Chef with shift schedule of 2pm to midnight', 'To excel in the full stack bootcamp course I needed to commit to an effective study schedule and find a workaround to stay connected with my team', 'First I made a study schedule outside my rest and work time, allocating hours study session each day. I made use of my weekend to meet up with my team for pair programming and the mentors for coding review.','The schedule helped me stay accountable to myself and effective. I was able to complete the set weekly coursework on time. In additional successful finish the final project with my team.', '2022/01/03', '2022/01/13');


title, situation, task, action, result, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (2, 1, 'Conflict Management', 'Tell us about a conflict you had with a cowork. How did you solve it?', 'During a project, a team member once felt that my way of tracking a project was wrong. He came off a bit harsh.','The object to maintain a team working enviorment', 'To manage siutation professionally, I politely asked him if he had a better suggestion. He tabled what he though, and we had a conversation as a team', 'We settled for his idea and recorded better results.','2022/01/03', '2022/01/13');

title, situation, task, action, result, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (3, 2, 'Team work', 'Share with us an experience where you motivated a fellow worker.', 'One of my fellow workmates once shared that she was tired and thinking of quitting her job when we were in the middle of a project.', 'when I asked her why she told me that demotivated.', 'I urged her to think about some of the successes she had experience in her career and even invited her to a motivation talk.', 'She managed to pull through and give her best till we completed the project, agter which she happily resigned to pursue other ventures.','2022/01/03', '2022/01/13');

title, situation, task, action, result, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (4, 3, 'Time Management', 'How do you work under pressure', 'At the coding bootcamp we had design a TV Show Website. At the same period I had several deadlines at my work.', 'To modified my study schedule.', 'I list all the activites required to acheive each deadline including the coding bootcamp project. Then I broke then to sub tasks with allocated time to completed the tasks', 'I sucessful met all deadlines and complete the TV project.','2022/01/03', '2022/01/13');

